### Register User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Akash",
  "email": "akash@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "address": "Chennai"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "akash@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}